### ==================== Email 邮件测试 ====================

### 发送简单邮件
POST http://localhost:8888/api/email/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "to": "customer@example.com",
  "toName": "Sijin",
  "subject": "Welcome to TeaTime Spa! 🎉",
  "textContent": "Thank you for joining us!",
  "htmlContent": "<h1>Welcome!</h1><p>Thank you for joining <strong>TeaTime Spa</strong>!</p>"
}

###

### 发送带附件的邮件
POST http://localhost:8888/api/email/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "to": "customer@example.com",
  "toName": "Sijin",
  "subject": "Your Invoice",
  "htmlContent": "<p>Please find your invoice attached.</p>",
  "attachments": [
    {
      "filename": "invoice.txt",
      "type": "text/plain",
      "base64Content": "SW52b2ljZSAjMTIzNDUKQW1vdW50OiAkMTAwLjAw"
    }
  ]
}

###

### 发送带 CC/BCC 的邮件
POST http://localhost:8888/api/email/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "to": "customer@example.com",
  "toName": "Sijin",
  "subject": "Team Update",
  "htmlContent": "<p>Here's the latest update...</p>",
  "cc": ["manager@example.com"],
  "bcc": ["admin@example.com"]
}

###

### 使用动态模板发送（需要先在 SendGrid 创建模板）
POST http://localhost:8888/api/email/send-template
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "to": "customer@example.com",
  "toName": "Sijin",
  "templateId": "d-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx",
  "dynamicData": {
    "first_name": "John",
    "booking_date": "2025-01-15",
    "service_name": "Deep Tissue Massage"
  }
}

###

### ==================== 预约相关邮件 ====================

### 发送预约确认邮件
POST http://localhost:8888/api/email/booking-confirmation
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerEmail": "customer@example.com",
  "customerName": "Sijin",
  "bookingId": "BK-2025-001234",
  "serviceName": "Deep Tissue Massage",
  "staffName": "Sarah Johnson",
  "date": "January 15, 2025",
  "time": "2:00 PM",
  "duration": "60 minutes",
  "price": "120.00",
  "address": "123 Spa Street, Suite 100, San Francisco, CA 94102",
  "locationUrl": "https://maps.google.com/?q=123+Spa+Street",
  "cancelUrl": "https://teatime.spa/cancel/BK-2025-001234"
}

###

### 发送预约提醒邮件
POST http://localhost:8888/api/email/booking-reminder
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerEmail": "customer@example.com",
  "customerName": "Sijin",
  "bookingId": "BK-2025-001234",
  "serviceName": "Deep Tissue Massage",
  "staffName": "Sarah Johnson",
  "date": "Tomorrow, January 15",
  "time": "2:00 PM",
  "duration": "60 minutes",
  "address": "123 Spa Street, Suite 100, San Francisco, CA 94102"
}

###

### ==================== 支付相关邮件 ====================

### 发送支付收据
POST http://localhost:8888/api/email/payment-receipt
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerEmail": "customer@example.com",
  "customerName": "Sijin",
  "transactionId": "TXN-2025-567890",
  "items": [
    { "name": "Deep Tissue Massage (60 min)", "amount": 120.00 },
    { "name": "Aromatherapy Add-on", "amount": 25.00 },
    { "name": "Tip", "amount": 30.00 }
  ],
  "total": 175.00,
  "paymentMethod": "Visa ending in 4242",
  "date": "January 15, 2025"
}

###

### ==================== 批量发送（营销邮件） ====================

### 批量发送促销邮件
POST http://localhost:8888/api/email/send-bulk
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subject": "🎁 Special Offer Just for You!",
  "htmlContent": "<h1>Hi {{name}}!</h1><p>Enjoy 20% off your next visit!</p><p>Use code: <strong>SAVE20</strong></p>",
  "recipients": [
    {
      "email": "john@example.com",
      "name": "John",
      "customData": { "discount_code": "JOHN20" }
    },
    {
      "email": "jane@example.com",
      "name": "Jane",
      "customData": { "discount_code": "JANE20" }
    },
    {
      "email": "bob@example.com",
      "name": "Bob",
      "customData": { "discount_code": "BOB20" }
    }
  ]
}

###